<br>
The real subject is whether SZ trascends those flaws and provides a unique EQ experince that is challenging and enjoyable.<br>
<br>
In reality it will be more than challenging, leveling up as a non evil will be a daunting task and is most difficult, very far from challenging as only a few will run the gauntlet to lvl 20.  This isnt a positive challenge that is rewarding.  Its a brutal hazing on the start of period of verbal assaults, lvl 55's who will sit in a lvl 1-5 area repeatedly killing you over and over, and make your playing experince anything but what it is "advertised" as in the orginal post.<br>
